# Production API URL — set this in the Vercel dashboard (Project Settings →
# Environment Variables → Production). It overrides this file.
#
# IMPORTANT: use the Render backend ORIGIN ONLY. The generated API client
# already prepends "/api/v1" to every request, so do NOT add it here.
#   Correct: https://fastskeleton-api.onrender.com
#   Wrong:   https://fastskeleton-api.onrender.com/api/v1  (=> /api/v1/api/v1/...)
VITE_API_URL=
